{"tid":2353730,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇ching入黎一齊傾下廣東話？","createTime":"2021-01-05T03:25:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T13:40:05.000Z","uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a09010c439d3f73e97b3e74d44761aaa46ddd130","tid":2353730,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T03:25:54.000Z","msg":"香港人講嘅係變種廣州話嚟。<br />\n不過家陣廣州人變晒&quot;撈鬆&quot;（lao shong~外省人）<br />\n好多正確發音都失傳。<br />\n加上香港人生活節奏急速，講嘢都因為貪快出現懶音。<br />\n行山銀河~恆生銀行<br />\n巴士贊~巴士站<br />\n幼落~有落<br />\n殿啞~電話<br />\n岡復~光復<br />\n山實~三十"},{"pid":"b057333af9c125ac13b596f3103bd7e231abe71b","tid":2353730,"uid":226231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T03:26:36.000Z","msg":"岡復香港"},{"pid":"d7b3a2fe6de6e98a01f5ebd98b0671a7230dd6ee","tid":2353730,"uid":311626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T03:27:34.000Z","msg":"體育台深黃手足＝波台狗"},{"pid":"cd5dd5c8b7c192a3bc8c3a56b3e171fa6a222e07","tid":2353730,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b057333af9c125ac13b596f3103bd7e231abe71b","tid":2353730,"uid":226231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T03:26:36.000Z","msg":"岡復香港"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T03:28:14.000Z","msg":"ching邊到鄉下(廈)？"},{"pid":"3a2caa0cc2423325973ec63ca6dff12db16762db","tid":2353730,"uid":226231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd5dd5c8b7c192a3bc8c3a56b3e171fa6a222e07","tid":2353730,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b057333af9c125ac13b596f3103bd7e231abe71b","tid":2353730,"uid":226231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T03:26:36.000Z","msg":"岡復香港"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T03:28:14.000Z","msg":"ching邊到鄉下(廈)？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T03:28:37.000Z","msg":"大劣"},{"pid":"b1d9eddfcfda9a876144c4f54b807950d578f8c0","tid":2353730,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T03:30:22.000Z","msg":"樓主波台狗+熱狗"},{"